the
price range of exxonmobil common stock is as reported on the composite tape of
the several u.s. exchanges where exxonmobil commonstock is traded. the
principal market where exxonmobil common stock (xom) is traded is the new york
stock exchange, although the stockis traded on other exchanges in and
outside the united states.
